cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.SI, cs.DC 

The paper discusses the security and privacy challenges in the domain name system (DNS), which is a critical component of network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
